{"tid":2100431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 荷警搗破貨櫃「酷刑室」 手銬牙醫凳施虐","createTime":"2020-07-09T04:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T05:11:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3b4b60d76ed7cd8718157f8e7c946f2d49d4b05a","tid":2100431,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"荷蘭警方在鹿特丹南部搗破7個被改裝成隔音「酷刑室」貨櫃，內部有牙醫凳、手銬和手術刀等工具，相信是犯罪集團打算用來執行私刑，6名涉案人士被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警員獲取一名40歲海牙男子的信息後，發現貨櫃位置後持續監視，「酷刑室」快要完工時，警方展開拘捕行動，成功阻止有預謀的綁架、挾持人質及其他嚴重暴力罪行。檢察官辦公室指，每個貨櫃均設有隔音板及隔熱箔，有手銬安裝在天花板及地上，用以綁起「人質」，其中一個貨櫃放有加設手鐐及腳鐐的牙醫椅，相信是用來虐待受害人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2690473/荷警搗破貨櫃「酷刑室」%20手銬牙醫凳施虐\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2690473%2F%E8%8D%B7%E8%AD%A6%E6%90%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E3%80%8C%E9%85%B7%E5%88%91%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%8D%2520%E6%89%8B%E9%8A%AC%E7%89%99%E9%86%AB%E5%87%B3%E6%96%BD%E8%99%90&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=33d13fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2690473/荷警搗破貨櫃「酷刑室」%20手銬牙醫凳施虐</a>"},{"pid":"cf97af7d2a4f4663877fe58cf402f248774cd5e8","tid":2100431,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1739a15b51ea9831bd3f87cfd90700893ed216a","tid":2100431,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"買家係邊個"},{"pid":"c3730139bf360746014cea8442c1a31de95096ed","tid":2100431